<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="抗疫剧《在一起》定档，海报设计超用心！" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-390145" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/uisdc-ky-20200924-15.jpg" width="1500" height="767" /></span></p>
